Hi <@U03KAK3R4GY> the weird is that the results were saved in a few tests (_screenshot_) but I still can’t figure out in what moment because the same code didn’t work anymore.

So I understand that I’ll have to change the quiz structure, isn’t it? It’s now made as a custom module, with hubl and javascript.

<@U06DEQHLLS1> To fix this, you need to update the hidden field value before submitting the form. You can do this in two ways: either add an "onBeforeFormSubmit" event to the form, or attach an "onChange" event to the last required question in the quiz.
